<lyrics>[V1]
 Jaratýshym, Qutqarýshym,
 Janymdy men Saǵan baǵyshtaımyn.
 Adasqan edim, qara túnekte
 Jaryq bop nuryńdy tóktiń Qutqarýshym.

[C1]
   Alǵys Saǵan Isa!
   Tabynamyn men Iem.
   Alǵys Saǵan Isa, Qutqarýshym.</lyrics>
